Paper: hep-th/9312187

Date: 1993-12-23

Title: $N=1$ from $N=2$ Superstrings

Authors: Nobuyoshi Ohta and Jens Lyng Petersen

Comments: 7 pages, Latex file, NBI-HE-93-76

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B325 (1994) 67-70

We give a simple proof that a particular class of $N=2$ superstrings areequivalent to the $N=1$ superstrings. This is achieved by constructing asimilarity transformation which transforms the $N=2$ BRST operators into adirect sum of the BRST operators for the $N=1$ string and topological sectors.